Delaware Attorney General Said to Investigate Mortgage Database MERS

-- B y   D a v i d   M c L a u g h l i n
-- 
2011-07-26T16:28:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-26/delaware-attorney-general-said-to-investigate-mortgage-database-mers.html
The Delaware Attorney General’s
office is investigating a national mortgage database known as
MERS, according to a person familiar with the matter.  The Massachusetts Attorney General’s office is also
conducting a probe into the business, it said yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
